8. `r3t = new_r3 * t0b_packed` (1 mul)
9. `p0 = new_r0 + r1t` (1 add)
10. `p1 = new_r0 - r1t` (1 sub)
11. `p2 = new_r2 + r3t` (1 add)
12. `p3 = new_r2 - r3t` (1 sub)

4 muls, 4 adds, 4 subs = 12 ops per packed group × 16 groups = 192 ops per mega-block.

